.dropIndex() is the method responsible for removing an undesired index:

db.collection.dropIndex("Index name")


> db.movies.dropIndex("Worldwide Gross_1")
{ "nIndexesWas" : 5, "ok" : 1 }

> db.movies.dropIndex("IMDB Votes_1_Worldwide Gross_1")
{ "nIndexesWas" : 4, "ok" : 1 }

> db.movies.dropIndex("Title_1_Worldwide Gross_1")
{ "nIndexesWas" : 3, "ok" : 1 }
> 